USAGE LICENSE: [trending audio with credit / royalty-free / custom / brand-supplied]
TEMPO: [exact BPM range]
KEY ENERGY: [building / sustained / dropping / cyclical]
HOOK MOMENT: [exact second where music peak lands — must align with frame pivot]
DUCK POINTS: [exact seconds where music drops -12dB for VO]
EXIT BEHAVIOR: [fades / cuts / drops to silence / lingers]
```

MUSIC-PILLAR MATCHING:

PILLAR 1 (Modern Minimalist Luxe): ambient electronica / Nils Frahm / minimal piano / 70-100 BPM
PILLAR 2 (Editorial Bold): power-anthem / synth-bold / drums-driven / 110-130 BPM
