### AG.1 — THE PRINCIPLE

Color grading is the final 20% that takes a reel from looking captured to looking directed. The directive currently names colorist references (Deakins, Lubezki, etc.) — this part adds technical color grade specs the engine writes per reel for finer control.

### AG.2 — THE COLOR GRADE BLOCK

