  - Saturation: [+X% / -X%]
  - Rolloff: [hard / soft / film-print]
  - Detail in highlights: [retained / clipped / lifted]
MIDTONES:
  - Hue shift: [exact direction]
  - Saturation: [+X% / -X%]
